{"tid":149440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於高鐵一地兩檢存有唔少疑問","createTime":"2017-03-09T09:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T11:12:42.000Z","uid":61197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc8f50b7d48b3d5546a666285012690f517c049","tid":149440,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"一.<br />\n中國政府使用本港土地洗唔洗好似后海灣口岸咁支付租金? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n二.<br />\n我個人覺得呢個係最好,以我所知香港高鐵站係一條支線,反而深圳北站係一個高鐵總站(所以起到成為亞洲最大嘅車站), 咁其實喺深圳北站落車本身都有需要,所以順便過埋境完全係冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20150510/19142503\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20150510%2F19142503&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn08VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0480576e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20150510%2F19142503&h=a6918b35\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20150510/19142503</a><br />\n<br />\n三.<br />\n其實基本法好清晰列明中國法律香港不適用,解釋法律都冇用<br />\n<br />\n四.<br />\n其實而家香港去中國廣東省境內直通車/巴士其實都快咗, 因為多咗好多highway, 而據我所知,廣深港高鐵係唔會出到廣東省,所以正如我第二點所講,香港人搭高鐵,本身都有喺深圳北落車嘅需要,我覺得反而係深圳北站設關更好,而且喺香港賣去中國唔同地方嘅車飛,乘客去到深圳北站過關後再按需要轉乘, 咁樣我覺得更有效率,反正如果一地兩檢係香港搞,高鐵嘅效能反而減低<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7042417b09752f1b5c4b34ea6fa1cc3f39de5641","tid":149440,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:55:20.000Z","msg":"強推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddaf4031255d7bdfaeac00fa1488a89834ae3b40","tid":149440,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:59:48.000Z","msg":"第3點- 佢而家係要幾指定區域割地，變做中國領土。（類似領事館既做法）<br />\n佢地咁借咁樣黎繞過基本法18條，要做既係阻止佢合法地割地。"},{"pid":"bbf6ca458824fbaf8539e55f2ccdb7e1f6dc324c","tid":149440,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:00:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第3點- 佢而家係要<span style=\"color: red;\">將</span>指定區域割地，變做中國領土。（類似領事館既做法）<br />\n佢地咁借咁樣黎繞過基本法18條，要做既係阻止佢合法地割地。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"59476cf04f224be48e0b7de22682709ac57f294f","tid":149440,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:03:12.000Z","msg":"仲有唔好跌入第一點既討論，冇意思。變相認同佢呢個做法<br />\n佢係西九龍割幾千尺出黎，計返市價咪最多每個月比二三十萬香港政府。"},{"pid":"fee742e08af569c5c6d0da414d200cfb86581f50","tid":149440,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:03:36.000Z","msg":"一向都話唔撚 work <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a5c2fa8b7551f6ea8c7c2efd5a4af66b8ace95","tid":149440,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第3點- 佢而家係要幾指定區域割地，變做中國領土。（類似領事館既做法）<br />\n佢地咁借咁樣黎繞過基本法18條，要做既係阻止佢合法地割地。</blockquote><br />\n但其實呢種割地方法有冇話一定要領事館用途, 定其實可以自由割?"},{"pid":"42685ed699da3415fbdcea5a3c80b025d8476724","tid":149440,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38374434202a887ba484ff8af8c2968b192f2235","tid":149440,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:04:29.000Z","msg":"其實無乜疑問 都唔會阻止到佢<br />\n記住中國產黨係依法辦事"},{"pid":"10c58b6615b2632523d8afe8f3c0fa830f5ab11f","tid":149440,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"大石紮死蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}